lead_paragraph: Titans coach Mike Mularkey simply wanted to win, so he chose to try a 2-point conversion in the closing minutes in Kansas City rather than let Ryan Succop kick the tying extra point.

headline.print_headline: Succop's 53-Yard Field Goal Gives Titans 19-17 Win Over KC
headline.main: Succop's 53-Yard Field Goal Gives Titans 19-17 Win Over KC
